line_1: And Master's Feet are swath'd no longer,
line_2: Again as She grows something stronger,

line_1: Make use of such Machine no longer;
line_2: When Members knit, and Legs grow stronger,

line_1: And in Fatigues can hold out longer;
When I've took the same Physic a Week or two longer.
line_2: But, without any Doubt, I shall find myself stronger,
